commitResults.messageBody:
No functionality to set a due date for a task

A task often may have a due date.

Added three classes as a blueprint to support a refined implementation of
this function, namely:
- Task.java
- SetDueDateCommand.java
- SetDueDateCommandParser.java

Three areas for a complete implementation:
- backend: logic, model, storage
- frontend: UI
- tests
